Class AbstractScheduler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.core.model.script.scheduler.test.AbstractScheduler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.quartz.Scheduler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockScheduler
    public abstract class AbstractScheduler
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.quartz.Scheduler
    Abstract Quartz Scheduler. This hides all of the methods that we don't need to implement, to make the {@see MockScheduler} class easier to read.
    Author:
    Jon Evans - Initial contribution
